\c 61
\s Dhavhidhi anovimba naMwari pakutambudzika kwake
\d Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. Nemutengeranwa. \add Pisarema\add* raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Inzwai, Mwari, kuchema kwangu; teererai kumunyengetero wangu\x + Map. 55.1,2.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Ndichadana kwamuri ndiri pamugumo wepanyika, kana moyo wangu wopera; nditungamirirei kudombo rakakwirira kundidarika\x + Map. 77.3.\x*.
\v 3 Nokuti manga muri utiziro hwangu\x + Map. 62.7,8. Map. 14.6.\x*, shongwe yakasimba kubva pamuvengi\x + Zvir. 18.10.\x*.
\v 4 Ndichagara mutende renyu rinhi narinhi\x + Map. 15.1. Map. 27.4.\x*; ndichatizira kunzvimbo yokuvanda yemapapiro enyu. Sera\x + Rut. 2.12.\x*.
\v 5 Nokuti imwi Mwari, makanzwa mhiko dzangu; maka\add ndi\add*pa nhaka yeavo vanotya zita renyu.
\v 6 Muchawedzera\x + Map. 21.4.\x* mazuva pamazuva amambo\x + Map. 63.11. Map. 84.9.\x*; makore ake achava sezera nezera.
\v 7 Achagara pamberi paMwari rinhi narinhi; mugadze ngoni nechokwadi \add kuti\add* zvimuchengete\x + Map. 40.11.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Naizvozvo ndichaimbira zita renyu rumbidzo kusvika rinhi narinhi, kuti ndizadzise mhiko dzangu zuva \add ne\add*zuva\x + Map. 50.14.\x*.